      <p>We don't cut corners. Each Volenu garment is the result of careful material selection, precise construction, and an obsessive attention to how fabric moves, drapes, and ages on the body.</p>
      <p>Our linen breathes. Our knitwear holds its shape. Our shirts carry a structured softness that you feel the moment you put them on and that others notice the moment you walk in.</p>
      <p>This is menswear built to last, designed to elevate, and priced so you can actually build a wardrobe worth having.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VALUES -->
